{"word":"H1058 - בָּכָה - bâkâh - baw-kaw' - [idiom] at all - எவ்விதத்திலும்","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>בָּכָה"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bâkâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>baw-kaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] at all / எவ்விதத்திலும்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அழு, துக்கங்கொண்டாடு, புலம்பு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to weep, to bewail, to cry, to shed tears"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to weep (in grief, humiliation, or joy)"},{"paragraph":"2) to weep bitterly (with cognate acc.)"},{"paragraph":"3) to weep upon (to em brace and weep)"},{"paragraph":"4) to bewail"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) participle"},{"paragraph":"1) lamenting"},{"paragraph":"2) bewailing"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>weep</i>; generally to <i>bemoan: - </i> X at all, bewail, complain, make lamentation, X more, mourn, X sore, X with tears, weep."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1058 - בָּכָה - bâkâh - baw-kaw'/1058\">H1058</a>, <a href=\"#/H1059 - בֶּכֶה - bekeh - beh'-keh/1059\">H1059</a>, <a href=\"#/H1065 - בְּכִי - Bᵉkîy - bek-ee'/1065\">H1065</a>, <a href=\"#/H1066 - בֹּכִים - Bôkîym - bo-keem'/1066\">H1066</a>, <a href=\"#/H1068 - בְּכִית - bᵉkîyth - bek-eeth'/1068\">H1068</a>, <a href=\"#/H439 - אַלֹּון בָּכוּת - ʼAllôwn Bâkûwth - al-lone' baw-kooth'/439\">H439</a>"}]}